    "For example, in Generative Agents [20], memory streams are updated after performing actions within the system.",
    "SayCan [78] enables agents to take actions to update understandings of the environment.",
    "(3) Triggering new actions.",
    "In the task completion process, one agent action can be triggered by another one.",
    "For example, Voyager [38] constructs buildings once it has gathered all the necessary resources."
